<div class="dablink">This article is about the People's Republic of China.  For Iran's Islamic Cultural Revolution, see <a href="/wiki/Iran%27s_Cultural_Revolution_of_1980-1987" title="Iran's Cultural Revolution of 1980-1987" class="mw-redirect">Iran's Cultural Revolution of 1980-1987</a>.</div>
